{# 
  Advanced Feedback Prompt Template
  Features:
    - Contextual intro based on cycle count
    - Dynamic previous issues/comments section
    - Optional comments, rationale, and debug mode
    - Strict output format instruction
    - Localization support
#}

{% if cycle_count is defined and cycle_count == 1 %}
Welcome to your first feedback cycle! Your input will help us improve the generated requirements and documentation.
{% else %}
Cycle {{ cycle_count | default("N/A") }} Feedback:
{% endif %}

{% if prev_issues is defined and prev_issues %}
Previously, you noted these issues:
{% for issue in prev_issues %}
- {{ issue }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

Please rate the **clarity** and **coverage** of the most recent generated requirements and documentation.

- Provide a **score between 0 (poor) and 1 (excellent)**.
- {{ "Comments are optional." if allow_comments else "No additional comments required." }}

{% if custom_focus is defined and custom_focus %}
Special focus for this cycle: {{ custom_focus }}
{% endif %}

IMPORTANT:  
Return your feedback as a **single, valid JSON object** with these keys:
```json
{
  "score": <float, 0 to 1>,
  {% if allow_comments %}"comments": "<your comments here>",{% endif %}
  {% if ask_rationale %}"rationale": "<brief explanation of your score>",{% endif %}
  "improvement_suggestions": "<optional: how could the requirements/docs be better?>"
}